✅ STEP 6: Save and Test
Save the file (Ctrl + S)

In terminal, run: streamlit run app.py

Test with a photo

Make sure sidebar appears and button works

📤 STEP 7: Send Back Your Work
Find app.py in your folder

Right-click → Send to → Compressed (zipped) folder

Send the ZIP file to your project leader

🆘 If Something Breaks
Undo your last change and test again

